#

Avocado Salsa Verde Chicken

35 min
$15
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh Protein

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Main

Tags:

EasyHealthyMexican

Description

Juicy chicken breast topped with a fresh and creamy avocado salsa for a burst of flavor!

Ingredients

  • chicken breast: 2 pieces
  • avocado: 1 ripe
  • tomato: 1 medium
  • red onion: 1/4 small
  • cilantro: 1/4 cup
  • lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: 1/2 teaspoon
  • cumin: 1/2 teaspoon
